ges.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-30.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2878\" height=\"1386\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ChatGPT\u0026#39;s software giving me honest answers in the app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-30.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-30.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e Once I\u0026#39;ve put these instructions into the chat (or project), I\u0026#39;m more likely to get honest responses for future parts of the conversation. Sometimes, the memory updates; if it does, I re-enter the prompt.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"asking-chatgpt-for-conflicting-opinions\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e4 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Asking ChatGPT for Conflicting Opinions\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eI\u0026#39;ve noticed that if I use ChatGPT too much without it disagreeing with me, the tool becomes more detrimental than beneficial. If I\u0026#39;m having a conversation and discussing ideas, the constant agreement also starts to wear on me. While the software has sometimes called me out without needing anything to, I often have to enter the prompt myself.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2878\" height=\"1396\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ChatGPT creating a list of pros and cons in the app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-10-59.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e Besides asking the tool to disagree with me so I don\u0026#39;t become too full of myself, I\u0026#39;ll also ask for conflicting opinions when I\u0026#39;m debating a certain decision. For example, this tactic works really well when I\u0026#39;m thinking about whether to add a new digital tool to my life or keep my toolkit streamlined.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnderstanding when ChatGPT is being too agreeable and taking action when needed is one \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/stop-ai-chatbot-agreement/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eway I stop AI chatbots from agreeing with me all the time\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"telling-chatgpt-to-go-into-quot-roast-mode-quot\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Telling ChatGPT to Go Into \u0026#34;Roast Mode\u0026#34;\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eI first realized ChatGPT could be quite funny when \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/chatgpt-hot-takes-wild-responses/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003easking the software for some hot takes\u003c/a\u003e. Since then, some of the responses it has given me have been… interesting, to say the least. Telling the software to go into Roast Mode often gives me some brutally honest (and somewhat edgy) results, which makes using the tool more interesting.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eMost of the time, ChatGPT goes into Roast Mode if I give a prompt with a brutally honest opinion. This particularly works in projects where I\u0026#39;ve done this before (by the way, \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/how-use-chatgpt-projects-boost-productivity/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eProjects is the most underrated ChatGPT feature\u003c/a\u003e). The app has more context from other conversations when I use this version.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2878\" height=\"1380\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asking ChatGPT to Roast \" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-12-57.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e Sometimes, the software updates its memory and doesn\u0026#39;t give the responses I want. When it does this, I just provide the instructions on how to enter Roast Mode.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"asking-chatgpt-to-play-the-role-of-an-expert\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e2 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Asking ChatGPT to Play the Role of an Expert\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile I sometimes need to explicitly tell ChatGPT to be more honest, I don\u0026#39;t always have to resort to this. Sometimes, telling the software to play the role of an expert is good enough.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1793\" height=\"912\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A recipe from the expert chef that is ChatGPT.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024-11-19_15h58_49.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e I\u0026#39;ll often tell ChatGPT to be an expert when asking for help with planning my goals. For example, if I were trying to put together a gym routine, I may tell the tool to pretend it\u0026#39;s a personal trainer or nutritionist.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eAsking ChatGPT to be an expert is generally \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/how-get-best-chatgpt-answers-expert-prompts/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ethe best way to get better prompts\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"telling-chatgpt-to-disagree-with-me-in-instructions\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Telling ChatGPT to Disagree With Me in Instructions\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile ChatGPT is good with conflicting opinions when asked, it sometimes still agrees with me (or gives both sides of the story). So, when I\u0026#39;m looking for thoughts from the other side, I\u0026#39;ll ask ChatGPT to disagree with me. Doing so is much easier than having a discussion on social media since it tends not to resort to insults.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eI\u0026#39;ll sometimes put this instruction in projects, but on other occasions, it\u0026#39;ll just go in the prompt. Occasionally, I will play devil\u0026#39;s advocate and continue asking conflicting questions—but in other instances, I\u0026#39;ll just try and get a more detailed answer.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2880\" height=\"1392\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asking ChatGPT to disagree in the app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/screenshot-2025-06-25-at-13-48-24.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e While ChatGPT can seem like a robotic golden retriever that wants to please, you can make the tool more honest. It\u0026#39;ll sometimes go full-on Roast Mode, but on other occasions, you can get respectful disagreeing responses. Using each of these has made the app more fun to use and also improved the quality of each response I get.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
